data.description: This lovely single family home was recently built in just 2019. Features include Quartz countertops, an open floor plan, high vaulted ceilings, beautiful wood floors, a large primary bedroom with a walk-in shower, and a fully fenced in back yard with a patio. The Wild Horse subdivision offers great amenities such as tennis courts, a pool, and a play area. Come look for yourself today!
